                        },
                        "displayName": "Wes McKinney",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "America/New_York"
                    },
                    "body": "Closing as Won't Fix. The release verification process is regularly turning up issues that would be occluded by a Dockerized build (e.g. I found several problems on Ubuntu 14.04 for 0.12)\r\n\r\nI think we should definitely make it more straightforward / simpler to set up the user environment to run the script though",
